23-// US-040 — Campaign detail screen. Gated under the creator tab group so
24-// the shared TabBar stays visible; route matches the story AC
25-// (`app/(creator)/listing/[id].tsx`). Data flows through the
26-// get-listing-detail edge function (US-039) — that path is picked
--
43-//     eligible + !active-app  → ButtonPrimary "Apply to collab"
44-//     eligible + active-app   → StatusPill + disabled CTA
45-//     ineligible              → disabled CTA "Not eligible yet"
46-//     inactive listing        → no CTA, status banner at top
47-//
